import React from 'react';
import RepositoryItem from '../repository-item';
import * as S from './styled';

const Repositories = () => {

  return (
    <S.WrapperTabs
      selectedTabClassName='is-selected'
      selectedTabPanelClassName='is-selected'
    >
      <S.WrapperTabList>
        <S.WrapperTab>Repositories</S.WrapperTab>
        <S.WrapperTab>Starred</S.WrapperTab>
      </S.WrapperTabList>
      <S.WrapperTabPanel>
        <RepositoryItem 
          name="app-curriculo"
          linkToRepo="https://github.com/BrunoMundim/app-curriculo"
          fullName="BrunoMundim/app-curriculo"
        />
      </S.WrapperTabPanel>
      <S.WrapperTabPanel>
        <RepositoryItem 
          name="Dio-Inter-Frontend-Developer"
          linkToRepo="https://github.com/BrunoMundim/Dio-Inter-Frontend-Developer"
          fullName="BrunoMundim/Dio-Inter-Frontend-Developer"
        />
      </S.WrapperTabPanel>
    </S.WrapperTabs>
  );
}

export default Repositories;
